title: Jocko Podcast #4: RENDEZVOUS WITH DEATH, Disrespect, Workouts
description:
Navy SEAL, Jocko Willink and Director, Echo Charles discuss the poem, "Rendezvous", and the book, "Battle Leadership" (Adolf Von Schell).. Answer internet questions and also converse about encountering disrespect, workouts, and leading one's self. 

Available on iTunes and Stitcher.

1:07:32  -  Internet Questions
